{"word":"G3140 - μαρτυρέω - martyréō - mar-too-reh'-o - Charge","slug":"G3140","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μαρτυρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>martyréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mar-too-reh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Charge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03C4;&#x03C5;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - martureo&#x0304;</b> - <i>mar-too-reh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3144\">G3144</a>; to <i>be a witness</i>, that is, <i>testify</i> (literally or figuratively): - charge, give [evidence], bear record, have (obtain, of) good (honest) report, be well reported of, testify, give (have) testimony, (be, bear, give, obtain) witness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1263\">G1263</a>, <a href=\"#/G1957\">G1957</a>, <a href=\"#/G2649\">G2649</a>, <a href=\"#/G3141\">G3141</a>, <a href=\"#/G3142\">G3142</a>, <a href=\"#/G3143\">G3143</a>, <a href=\"#/G3144\">G3144</a>, <a href=\"#/G4303\">G4303</a>, <a href=\"#/G4828\">G4828</a>, <a href=\"#/G4901\">G4901</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577\">G5577</a>"}]}